# Chuk MCP PowerPoint Server

A powerful, LLM-friendly PowerPoint design system with MCP server integration. Built with shadcn-inspired component architecture, featuring variants, composition patterns, and comprehensive theming.

## âœ¨ Highlights

- **ğŸ¨ Design System** - shadcn/ui-inspired component architecture
- **ğŸ­ Theme System** - 15+ built-in themes with dark/light modes
- **ğŸ§© Variant System** - Type-safe, composable variants (cva-inspired)
- **ğŸ”§ Composition Patterns** - Build complex UIs from subcomponents
- **ğŸ“‹ Component Registry** - LLM-friendly schemas and discovery
- **ğŸ¯ Design Tokens** - Consistent colors, typography, spacing
- **ğŸ¤– MCP Integration** - Full Model Context Protocol support
- **âœ… Fully Tested** - 1900+ tests with comprehensive coverage
- **â˜ï¸ Cloud Ready** - Deploy to Fly.io with Tigris S3 and Redis

